snippet.title: Labyrinth Of The Demon King ►Top Hat Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
A first person survival horror game with brutal melee combat, set in a world inspired by feudal Japan. Venture through the Labyrinth Of The Demon King, solving puzzles and fighting terrifying monsters, in an epic quest to track down the demon who betrayed your lord and end its life. Featuring PS1-style retro graphics, complete with dither filters and loading screen doors.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1804010/Labyrinth_Of_The_Demon_King/
